def rc4decrypt(c,key):
    s=[]
    t=[]
    for i in range(256):
        s.append(i)
    for i in range(256):
        t.append(ord(key[i%len(key)]))
    j=0
    for i in range(256):
        j=(j+s[i]+t[i])%256
        s[i],s[j]=s[j],s[i]
    i=0
    j=0
    flag=[]
    for k in range(len(c)):
        i=(i+1)%256
        j=(j+s[i])%256
        s[i], s[j] = s[j], s[i]
        x=(s[i]+s[j])%256
        flag.append(c[k]^(s[x]+2))
    return flag
